


Tekify was an onsite computer repair computer service company that provided services to Davis and surrounding areas.  They provided bestinclass service and support to both business and residential clients.  No matter how big or small the challenge, Tekify would have your computer and network up and running like new in no time.  They had experience with almost every computer problem imaginable, including virus removal and prevention, setting up networks, printers, voiceoverIP telephone systems, server setup and maintenance, and so much more.  Tekify offers regular fixit type services as well as a flatrate proactive network monitoring and management plan for businesses who cannot have computer system downtime.

